list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment:
Added log function for debugging.
The log function can write to console.log(), print(), or localStorage. The localStorage logging can be to a single key ('proscriptls_log'), or to a ring of entries (default size is 50), 'proscriptls_log:0' to 'proscriptls_log:49', current position stored in localStorage with key 'proscripls_log:current'. The ring can be dumped in the browser dev window using dumpWriteLogRing(). Added wam_log and wam_log_size to prolog flags in foreign.js. Added call to log using prolog_flag_values.wam_log of decode_instruction() for current instruction. Added clear_local_storage_log/0 to clear both 'proscriptls_log' key item and ring items in localStorage.

task.summary:
Added localStorage and memoryFile coordination.
Added save_tiles/0 and load_tiles/0 to tiles.pl. Added save_data/2, save_data/3, load_data/2, and remove_data/2 to data_predicates.pl. Data is saved to localStorage on the Window Web API object using a key constructed from a specified label plus the data predicate module and prefix. The data is saved as a Prolog-compilable collection of facts for each suffix of the specified prefix. Saving the data writes these facts to a memory file, then copies the memory file to the local storage. Loading the data reads the contents of local storage at a given key to a memory file, then compiles the contents of that memory file. memory_files.js: Fixed text_to_memory_file function to set the 'ptr' to the length of the byteArray (same as if the text had been written to the memory file); fixed open_memory_file to set 'ptr' to 0 on read and write modes and data.length on append mode (added 'append' mode); refactored to create valie_memfile; and added predicate_copy_memory_file_to_local_storage and predicate_copy_local_storage_to_memory_file functions. object.js: added storage, windowlocalstorage, and windowsessionstorage API interfaces; and fixed convert_type_term handling of arrayType - expects 'array_type' instead of 'array'. object_method.js: fixed predicate_dom_object_method to properly fail when multiple-return method result is 'null'. promise.js: refactored get_promise_object; changed promise_requests map to hold the promiseResultJS. Fixed quote_atom in read.js to quote atoms that start with a digit (0 to 9). web_interfaces.js: Added Storage, WindowLocalStorage, and WindowSessionStorage Web API interfaces. Added export of compile_and_free_memory_file/1 to wam_compiler.pl. Added builtin definitions for copy_memory_file_to_local_storage/2 and copy_local_storage_to_memory_file/2 to wam_bootstrap.pl. Added web_test_blob and web_test_window to web_tests.pl.

Added retract_all_data/1 and retract_all_data/2 to data_predicates.pl.
Fixed retract_data/2 to process nested modules. Added performance cuts to nth0/3, nth0/4, nth1/3, and nth1/4.

Added retracting and writing of data-predicates default ID.
Changed data_predicates.pl to retract the default ID before loading data and to write the default ID when saving data. Changed compile_memory_file/1 to cut at the end of the clause to ensure no backtracking occurs after the compilation.

Fixed X =.. [X] for trivial constant values of X.
Fixed wam_compiler to properly handle aux_definition compilations where the first goal has multiple arguments. These definitions are used in several builtins, e.g. setup_call_catch_cleanup, \+, and forall. This bug caused tests.pl test univ(9) to fail. Created dumpCode function in dump.js. Refactored decode_instruction.js to create decode_instruction_general function and opNames global; created predicate_decode_instruction for decode_instruction/4 builtin. Added decode_instructions/2 to bootstrap_js.pl. Fixed first_goal_arity/2 in wam_compiler.pl to handle post-transformation goals of the form goal(G). Added several tests to test.pl for new univ cases.
Optimized pop_current_compilation_stream/1 by cutting retract/1 choices.
Optimized pop_current_compilation_module/1 by cutting retract/1 choices.

Added save_data_stream/2, changed tiles.pl to save data in a single key.
tiles.pl: changed save_tiles/0 to use save_data_stream/2 instead of save_data/2; changed load_tiles/0 to call retract_all_data/1 and load data from a single localStorage key. data_predicates.pl: added retract_all_data/1, save_data_stream/2, save_data_stream/3; fixed write of predicate comment to before gather_data for IDs. object.pl: fixed associativity for several operators; extended basic predicates >>/2, >->/2, >+>/2, >*>/2, and >@>/2 to allow object expression in first argument; renamed base predicates to general_application/2, attribute_application/2, property_application/2, method_application/2, and goal_application/2; added object_expression/2, bottom_right/2, and evaluate_expression/1. Fixed promise.js error messages. Fixed read_expression function in read.js to handle 'yfx' associativity correctly. Added type checking in recorded function in record.js. Fixed hex function in wam.js to check type of 'number' parameter to avoid possible bug in Safari. Added yield/0 predicate to bootstrap_js.pl. Also changed call/1 to call wam_compiler:pop_current_compilation_module before the '!, $jmp' sequence. Changed use of assertion of '$current_compilation_module'/1 and '$current_compilation_stream'/1 to use recording key wam_compiler_compilation_modules and wam_compiler_compilation_stream. Added test_local_storage .html and .pl. Added leftassoc and rightassoc tests to tests.pl.

Fixed object.pl modules in >+>/2 and >->/2. Fixed current_prolog_flag.
Adjusted values for flag_min_integer and flag_max_integer. Added debug output for each clause to compile_stream_term/3 controlled by current_prolog_flag debug = on. The output is followed by a yield/0 call to allow the debug text to be written immediately. Added flag unit test. Fixed web_test*.pl to remove singleton variables. Fixed 'class of test1 finds 1 classes [foo, bar]' to use setof/3 instead of findall/3.

Extended dynamic directive to allow explicit module and lists.
Added game_data_x.pl. Removed unused x_history and h_ptr global vars from proscript_interpreter_terminal.js.
